'''El Minya Sporting Club''' ({{lang-ar|نادي المنيا للألعاب الرياضية}}), is an [[Egypt]]ian football club based in [[Minya, Egypt|El Minya]], Egypt. The club is currently playing in the [[Egyptian Second Division]], the second-highest league in the [[Football in Egypt|Egyptian football league system]].

