{{Infobox magazine | title = Idrottsarvet: årets bok | image_file = | image_size = | image_alt = | image_caption = | editor = [[Bo K. Karlsson]]<!-- Same as [[Bo Karlsson (football referee)]]?--> | editor_title = Editor | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | frequency = Yearly | circulation = | category = Sports | company = | publisher = [[Sports Museum (Gothenburg)|Sports Museum of Gothenburg]] | firstdate = 1986 | country = [[Sweden]] | based = [[Gothenburg]] | language = [[Swedish language|Swedish]] | website = http://www.idrottsmuseet.se/sidor/idrottsarvet.htm | issn = 0283-1791 }}
'''''Idrottsarvet: årets bok''''' (en: ''Sports Heritage: Year Book'') ({{ISSN|0283-1791}}) is a Swedish [[sport]] [[yearbook]] established in 1986. It is published annually by the [[Sports Museum (Gothenburg)|Sports Museum]] of [[Gothenburg]] (Idrottsmuseet i Göteborg), and edited by [[Bo W. Karlsson]]<!-- Same as [[Bo Karlsson (football referee)]]?-->.
