==L'Équipe awards (1994–2005)== Between 1994 and 2005, the French newspaper, [[L'Équipe]], also conducted a selection of the best French and foreign players of the league, through a vote of [[sports journalist|journalists]]. These awards are also considered official by the [[Ligue Nationale de Basket (LNB)]].
