'''Sportanlage Rheinwiese''' is a [[association football|football]] [[stadium]] in [[Schaan]], [[Liechtenstein]]. It is the home of [[FC Schaan]] and has a capacity of 1,500.
==See also== * [[List of football stadiums in Liechtenstein]]
